Chad Epperson will return for his fifth season as manager of the Portland Sea Dogs, as part of a coaching staff announced Friday by the Sea Dogs and the Boston Red Sox.

[![](https://www.pressherald.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/4/2026/01/38678291_20240606_baseball-betting_3_b96930.jpg?w=250&h=250&crop=1)](https://www.centralmaine.com/2025/08/19/in-portland-sea-dogs-manager-lays-groundwork-for-bostons-future/)

