Epperson, who holds the franchise record for wins by a manager, will be joined again by pitching coach Juan Rivera, assistant pitching coach Isaiah Page, defensive coach Kyle Sasala, trainer Bobby Stachura and strength and conditioning coach Jonah Mondloch. Newcomers to the staff are hitting coach Trevor Burmeister, assistant hitting coach Elijah Boyer and trainer Kelsey Branstetter.

